N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4226.5 - Parade to the post

State Regulations

All horses shall parade and, under penalty of
disqualification, shall carry their weight from the paddock to the starting
post, such parade to pass the finish line. Notes
